## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-197">异步搜索可显示发现结果，同时搜索更多结果。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-197">An asynchronous search can show results as they are found while simultaneously searching for additional results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-198">这对于填充列表框等任务非常有用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-198">This is useful for tasks such as populating list boxes.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-199">此属性的默认设置为 `false`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-199">The default setting for this property is `false`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-200">下面的 c # 示例演示如何创建异步搜索。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-200">The following C# example shows how to create an asynchronous search.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
//Set the Asynchronous property to true.  
src.Asynchronous = true;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-204">此属性设置为的特性必须是可分辨名称属性，例如 member 或 managedBy。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-204">The attribute that this property is set to must be a distinguished name attribute, such as member or managedBy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-205">属性可以是单值或多值属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-205">The attribute can be either single or multi-valued.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-206">有关详细信息，请参阅 [成员](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-member) 和 [管理](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-managedby) 的项目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-206">For more information, see the [Member](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-member) and [Managed-By](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-managedby) articles.</span></span>
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-207">针对由基对象的特性中指定的可分辨名称标识的对象执行搜索。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-207">The search is performed against the objects that are identified by the distinguished name that is specified in the attribute of the base object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-208">例如，如果基对象是一个 adschema 组类，并且 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> 设置为 "member"，则将对属于该组成员的所有对象执行搜索。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-208">For example, if the base object is an adschema group class and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> is set to "member," then the search will be performed against all objects that are members of the group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-209">有关详细信息，请参阅 [组类](/windows/desktop/adschema/c-group) 一文。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-209">For more information, see the [Group class](/windows/desktop/adschema/c-group) article.</span></span>
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-210"><xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A>使用属性时， <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> 属性必须设置为 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-210">When the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property is used, the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property must be set to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-211">如果将 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> 属性设置为任何其他值，则设置 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> 属性将引发 <xref:System.ArgumentException> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-211">If the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property is set to any other value, setting the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property will throw an <xref:System.ArgumentException>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-212">有关详细信息，请参阅 [执行属性范围查询](/windows/desktop/adsi/performing-an-attribute-scoped-query)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-212">For more information, see the [Performing an Attribute Scope Query](/windows/desktop/adsi/performing-an-attribute-scoped-query).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-213">下面的示例演示如何将 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> 属性与成员属性一起使用以获取组的成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-213">The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property with the member attribute to get the members of a group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-214">然后输出成员的名字和姓氏及其电话号码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-214">It then prints out the first and last names of the members and their telephone numbers.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;
using System.DirectoryServices;  

public class Example
{
    public static void Main()
    {
        DirectoryEntry group = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=MyGroup", …);        
        DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("(&(objectClass=user)(objectCategory=Person))");          
        src.AttributeScopeQuery = "member";  
        src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("sn");
        src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("givenName");  
        src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("telephoneNumber");  

        foreach(SearchResult res in src.FindAll())  
        {  
            Console.WriteLine("…");  
        }
    }
}
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-232">下面的 c # 示例演示如何将 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A> 属性设置为 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always> ，以便它在搜索下属和定位基对象时取消引用别名。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-232">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A> property to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always> , so that it dereferences aliases when both searching subordinates and locating base objects.</span></span>  
  
```  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher mySearcher = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
// Set DerefAlias to Always.  
src.DerefAlias = DereferenceAlias.Always;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-242">下面的示例演示如何以十六进制格式返回可分辨名称的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-242">The following example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-303">如果 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A> 是 Visual Basic) 中 (的空引用 `Nothing` ，则搜索根设置为服务器当前使用的域的根。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-303">If <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A> is a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), the search root is set to the root of the domain that your server is currently using.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-304">可以通过多种方式在全局目录中进行搜索：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-304">There are several ways to search in the global catalog:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-305">枚举全局目录并选择第一个子级。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-305">Enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-306">指定服务器名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-306">Specify the server name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-307">使用 DsGetDcName 函数查找全局编录。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-307">Use the DsGetDcName function to find the global catalog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-308">有关 DsGetDcName 函数的详细信息，请参阅 [dsgetdcname](/windows/win32/api/dsgetdc/nf-dsgetdc-dsgetdcnamea)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-308">For more information on the DsGetDcName function, see the [DsGetDcName](/windows/win32/api/dsgetdc/nf-dsgetdc-dsgetdcnamea).</span></span>
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-309">获取全局目录的 RootDSE，并要求 "rootNamingContext"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-309">Get the RootDSE  of the global catalog and ask for "rootNamingContext".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-310">使用全局编录，如使用 LDAP 一样指定搜索路径。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-310">Use the global catalog, specifying a search path as if using LDAP.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-311">例如，"GC://OU = ...，DC = ...，DC = ..."。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-311">For example, "GC://OU=..., DC=..., DC=...".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-312">下面的 c # 代码演示如何枚举全局目录并选择第一个子级。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-312">The following C# code shows how to enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
    ```csharp  
    DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("GC://forestname");  
    IEnumerator ie = entry.Children.GetEnumerator();  
    ie.MoveNext();  
    entry = (DirectoryEntry)ie.Current;  
    DirectorySearcher search = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
    ```

  
  
