 <span data-ttu-id="d75aa-350">下面的 c # 示例演示如何将 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> 属性设置为 `true` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d75aa-350">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
